    thereby quantitatively confirm the cautionary note by Brown et al. that KIC 
    estimates of [Fe/H] should not be used by "anyone with a particular interest in 
    stellar metallicities". Fortunately, many more LAMOST spectroscopic metallicities 
    will be available in the near future.},
